{"content": "I need to multiply 463 \u00d7 544 in base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n\n463\u2089 = 4\u00d79\u00b2 + 6\u00d79\u00b9 + 3\u00d79\u2070 = 4\u00d781 + 6\u00d79 + 3\u00d71 = 324 + 54 + 3 = 381\u2081\u2080\n\n544\u2089 = 5\u00d79\u00b2 + 4\u00d79\u00b9 + 4\u00d79\u2070 = 5\u00d781 + 4\u00d79 + 4\u00d71 = 405 + 36 + 4 = 445\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n\n381 \u00d7 445 = 381 \u00d7 (400 + 45) = 152,400 + 17,145 = 169,545\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n\n169545 \u00f7 9 = 18838 r 3\n18838 \u00f7 9 = 2093 r 1\n2093 \u00f7 9 = 232 r 5\n232 \u00f7 9 = 25 r 7\n25 \u00f7 9 = 2 r 7\n2 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 2\n\nReading from bottom to top: 277513\u2089\n\n**Step 4: Verification**\n\n277513\u2089 = 2\u00d759049 + 7\u00d76561 + 7\u00d7729 + 5\u00d781 + 1\u00d79 + 3\u00d71\n= 118098 + 45927 + 5103 + 405 + 9 + 3\n= 169,545\u2081\u2080 \u2713\n\n277513", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 1245, "completion_tokens": 442}